{"tid":2359062,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"Shopify : 特朗普縱容暴力組織，已即時關閉特朗普的官方網上商店 !","createTime":"2021-01-08T14:45:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T16:28:07.000Z","uid":219007,"like":1,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"63cdd944eb948505d715dc89d3c4a9dd2b9a027a","tid":2359062,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T14:45:01.000Z","msg":"（北美通訊）在美國社交媒體封殺特朗普之際，加拿大電商Shopify也跟隨宣佈，<a href=\"http://即時關閉特朗普的官方網上商店TrumpStore.com和特朗普競選團隊的官方網店shop.donaldjtrump.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E9%97%9C%E9%96%89%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E5%95%86%E5%BA%97TrumpStore.com%E5%92%8C%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E7%AB%B6%E9%81%B8%E5%9C%98%E9%9A%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E7%B6%B2%E5%BA%97shop.donaldjtrump.com&d=M%2BQ4vsyFJ%2Bls%2BsYkNkBEXYWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=b81fc5ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">即時關閉特朗普的官方網上商店TrumpStore.com和特朗普競選團隊的官方網店shop.donaldjtrump.com</a>，強調不會容忍煽動暴力的行為。<br />\n<br />\nShopify發言人在電郵中說，特朗普的行為違反了公司「可接受使用政策」 （Acceptable Use Policy），當中「禁止推廣或支持，威脅或縱容暴力的組織、平台或個人」。<br />\n<br />\n不過，電商巨擘亞馬遜（Amazon）和eBay拍賣網站仍在出售特朗普品牌商品。<br />\n<br />\n總部位於加拿大渥太華的Shopify於2004年創立，專為小企業提供網絡服務的公司，協助他們建立網站並向客戶銷售。隨着電子商務市場不斷擴大，該公司也吸引了不少大企業參加。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210108/G54CXCXFJVB5NLID5LBAU556RM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1RVKzBJnNDZyC5q0WbEN-q62i4XoxTkHNHHXP9rsll_CHa5ofYgV7w2BE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210108%2FG54CXCXFJVB5NLID5LBAU556RM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1RVKzBJnNDZyC5q0WbEN-q62i4XoxTkHNHHXP9rsll_CHa5ofYgV7w2BE&d=M%2BQ4vsyFJ%2Bls%2BsYkNkBEXYWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=c6aecd5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210108%2FG54CXCXFJVB5NLID5LBAU556RM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1RVKzBJnNDZyC5q0WbEN-q62i4XoxTkHNHHXP9rsll_CHa5ofYgV7w2BE&h=e6d781cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210108/G54CXCXFJVB5NLID5LBAU556RM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1RVKzBJnNDZyC5q0WbEN-q62i4XoxTkHNHHXP9rsll_CHa5ofYgV7w2BE</a>"},{"pid":"15749dc1aab32424cb1723d42ad56935edb7104d","tid":2359062,"uid":219007,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T14:47:39.000Z","msg":"全部打落水狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n政府換屆之後Trump肯定畀人告叛國罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9874526fae6f39cb7b5db58985c45286eb14d5eb","tid":2359062,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T14:49:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b5da1b04b3b739a80f5b68879d3abeb982e639","tid":2359062,"uid":254383,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T14:49:39.000Z","msg":"香港嗰班煽動721無人理"},{"pid":"33ea0082d28734e590a7c1a5606f849f23fd2faf","tid":2359062,"uid":324629,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"15749dc1aab32424cb1723d42ad56935edb7104d","tid":2359062,"uid":219007,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T14:47:39.000Z","msg":"全部打落水狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n政府換屆之後Trump肯定畀人告叛國罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T14:49:48.000Z","msg":"所以佢哋唔打內戰唔得"},{"pid":"7c71f411923f175db30968fc702f069c9d8cd74a","tid":2359062,"uid":53062,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T14:50:08